{"tid":1126521,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[終局之戰後]蜘蛛俠攜手 Mysterio？《Spider-Man: Far From Home》最新電影劇照釋出","createTime":"2019-04-26T12:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T14:36:13.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"099524b70f35e35b9bd2b148b9e17cd052aceeeb","tid":1126521,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/spider-man-far-from-home-summer-movie-preview-tom-holland\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F4%2Fspider-man-far-from-home-summer-movie-preview-tom-holland&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=c7aa5751\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/spider-man-far-from-home-summer-movie-preview-tom-holland</a><br />\n<br />\n《Spider-Man: Far From Home》將如何為 MCU 第三階段作結？<br />\n<br />\n本週曾報導 Marvel Studios 總裁 Kevin Feige 透露《Avengers: Endgame》並非是 MCU 第三階段的最終作品，而是將於暑假檔期上映的《Spider-Man: Far From Home》（蜘蛛俠: 決戰千里）來承擔這份重責。而 Tom Holland 所飾演的 Spider-Man 將於本集與朋友們一同前往歐洲旅遊，早前的電影海報就以倫敦，威尼斯和柏林等地為靈感作設計。<br />\n<br />\n而今番 Entertainment Weekly 最新公開的《Spider-Man: Far From Home》的電影劇照中，能發現知名演員 Jake Gyllenhaal 飾演的 Mysterio 或將與 Spider-Man 攜手合作，兩人的互動將成為本片的觀看重點。但 Mysterio 的定位其實亦正亦邪，依照漫畫設定他是反派，一名精通幻術和科技，認為擊敗 Spider-Man 便能出名的電影特技師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewGD6o8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewGD6o8.jpg&h=0832ef90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45da64dbc25e991efa31b75893c7448cfeb2ec84","tid":1126521,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRj2OCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRj2OCF.jpg&h=b23d0695&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d7b2b10bab44601a72130ced4171f9cbf1ebd05","tid":1126521,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3549ea42e29bb965ef9fc1e1805668eaf4e0a0","tid":1126521,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"多數扮好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61ad744d6b4e80f2312c658e678bfca6fe4ccba","tid":1126521,"uid":90499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"巴斯光年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}